labels.label: Load online master data to HBase

entry.value: SELECT question_id, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/account_id') AS VARCHAR) AS account_id, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/reputation') AS VARCHAR) AS reputation, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/user_id') AS VARCHAR) AS user_id, CAST(RPATH(owner, '/user_type') AS VARCHAR) AS user_type FROM FLOWFILE

SELECT is_answered, view_count, answer_count, score, last_activity_date, creation_date, question_id, title, CASE WHEN HAS_PATH(last_edit_date) THEN RPATH(FLOWFILE, '/last_edit_date') ELSE NULL END AS last_edit_date FROM FLOWFILE
